---
layout: base.njk
title: "Research — Mudun · Urban studies for Jordan"
description: "Two-layer research on Jordan's cities: a plain-language bilingual brief on top, the full study underneath. Mobility, walkability, public space, housing, transit."
---
{% import "entry-card.njk" as cardlib %}
  <section class="view active" id="view-research">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="label" data-en="Research" data-ar="الأبحاث"></span>
        <h2 data-en="Research on Jordan's cities" data-ar="أبحاثٌ عن مدن الأردن"></h2>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-top:1rem"
           data-en="Every piece has two layers: a plain-language brief — in both Arabic and English, with visuals — that anyone can read, and the full study underneath for those who want the detail."
           data-ar="لكلّ بحثٍ طبقتان: ملخّصٌ بلغة واضحة — بالعربية والإنجليزية، مع صور — يقرؤه الجميع، والدراسة الكاملة تحته لمن يريد التفاصيل."></p>
      </div>

      <div class="stack" style="margin-bottom:clamp(34px,5vw,52px)">
        <div class="layer brief">
          <div class="lt" data-en="Layer 1 — The brief" data-ar="الطبقة الأولى — الملخّص"></div>
          <strong data-en="Why it matters, key findings, and visuals" data-ar="لماذا يهمّ، وأبرز النتائج، والصور"></strong>
          <small data-en="Written by the researcher · in Arabic and English · a 3–5 minute read" data-ar="بقلم الباحث · بالعربية والإنجليزية · قراءة ٣–٥ دقائق"></small>
        </div>
        <div class="layer full">
          <div class="lt" data-en="Layer 2 — The full research" data-ar="الطبقة الثانية — البحث الكامل"></div>
          <strong data-en="The complete study (PDF)" data-ar="الدراسة الكاملة (PDF)"></strong>
          <small data-en="In the language it was written — methods, data, and citations" data-ar="باللغة التي كُتب بها — المنهجية والبيانات والمصادر"></small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="filters" data-filter-group aria-label="Categories">
        <button class="chip active" data-filter="all" data-en="All" data-ar="الكل"></button>
        <button class="chip" data-filter="mobility" data-en="Mobility" data-ar="التنقّل"></button>
        <button class="chip" data-filter="walk" data-en="Walkability" data-ar="المشي"></button>
        <button class="chip" data-filter="public" data-en="Public space" data-ar="الفضاء العام"></button>
        <button class="chip" data-filter="housing" data-en="Housing" data-ar="السكن"></button>
        <button class="chip" data-filter="transit" data-en="Transit" data-ar="النقل العام"></button>
      </div>

      <div class="entries">
{% for entry in collections.research %}{{ cardlib.card(entry, "research", categories) }}{% endfor %}
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:26px;color:var(--asphalt-soft);max-width:60ch"
         data-en="More research is on the way. If you study cities in Jordan, your work has a home here —"
         data-ar="المزيد من الأبحاث في الطريق. إن كنت تدرس مدن الأردن، فلعملك بيتٌ هنا —"></p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/publish/" style="margin-top:6px" data-en="Publish your research" data-ar="انشُر بحثك"></a>
    </div>
  </section>
